data.description: Gorgeous and bright 3 bedroom, 2 bath, 2 car garage Single Family Home in a luxurious 55+ gated community with 24/7 manned guard. Freshly painted, brand new A/C, tiled floors, split floor plan for privacy, formal dining & eat-in kitchen, brand-new stainless-steel appliances will be installed before closing, accordion shutters on all windows and sliding doors, foyer, high ceilings throughout the property, screened-in patio, walk-in closets, spacious dining room & living area overlooking the lake. Master bathroom is ADA equipped. Located on A CUL-DE SAC PRIVATE with LESS TRAFFIC. Spectacular location that's close to shopping centers and malls.HOA fee includes internet, landline, cable, monitored home security system, lawn maintenance, sprinklers, pressure wash roof and driveway.
